{"tid":988523,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「多圖遊記散文」越南 - 天梯 + 夜市","createTime":"2019-01-20T06:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T06:52:14.000Z","uid":231598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"304132e5c36e9872b0e00ccfa87402d3aadde303","tid":988523,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"Day6 大叻<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「越南天梯 + 夜市雜相」</span><br />\n<br />\n喺google map見到間sunny farm cafe ~7km<br />\n雖然架單車係幾廢下<br />\n但之前環台每日踩7x km都ok<br />\n咁短應該慢慢踩45分鐘都到啦<br />\n點知7km差唔多全程上斜<br />\n我落車堆嘅時間應為多過一半<br />\n仲要啲路又爛又亂又多車多廢氣<br />\n一路推一路喺度問自己點解要咁傻<br />\n點解唔俾幾十蚊搭grab<br />\n點解唔揸電單車<br />\n<br />\n終於到左Sunny Farm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcopNtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcopNtd.png&h=523175fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個人喺門口叫我擺低單車入去<br />\n我用把雞鎖鎖住個轆佢話唔洗<br />\n但我當然保障自己<br />\n架車冇左我喺越南賣屎忽都唔掂<br />\n但事後發現佢唔係想問我收錢<br />\n（佢地好中意幫你睇住架車，之後收番你3000-10000Vnd）<br />\n係純粹想幫我，話架車可以泊喺嗰度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時去旅行真係唔知應該幾信人<br />\n<br />\n影打卡相之前，<br />\n要一人買一杯野飲先俾入，<br />\n價錢大概35000-45000vnd（十幾蚊hkd）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cL6yFP5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcL6yFP5.png&h=ad08aa7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身覺得有啲貴<br />\n但飲左杯野一啖<br />\n再坐喺嗰度影下相，聽下歌<br />\n就覺得都值回票價<br />\n係一間幾舒服嘅cafe<br />\n唯一唔好就係真係離市區幾遠下<br />\n<br />\n望到呢個大叻景<br />\n就覺得頭先咁辛苦都係值得<br />\n辛苦過後嘅得來嘅野總係特別美好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXTEBp6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXTEBp6.png&h=5908efdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能喺你地眼中都冇乜特別<br />\n<br />\n呢條就係天梯<br />\n自己幻想下影出黎會係咩效果啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsJM0R0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsJM0R0.png&h=07e54af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐左成粒鐘就走人嚕<br />\n間野仲有其他景可以影下相<br />\n不過得有人嘅相我唔post出黎喇<br />\n<br />\n回程返市中心幾乎全落斜<br />\n話咁快就返到<br />\n<br />\n有一刻以為自己去左紐西蘭queenstown<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w43AUc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw43AUc3.png&h=25a1a4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有馬租你早響丫<br />\n踩到我咁辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvqcb0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcvqcb0c.png&h=11103b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還左車就返酒店梳洗下<br />\n夜晚又出左去行下<br />\n<br />\nRice pancake<br />\n一塊脆餅，有蛋、辣蝦米、肉碎、等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgkr0Un.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkgkr0Un.png&h=f29fc3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁多人賣士多啤梨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpnxWsU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpnxWsU.png&h=68c9f993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多人賣，應該幾甜，我都買左杯食<br />\n一杯都幾貴，20000VND（七蚊）<br />\n佢地多數會加啲yogurt，加啲唔知咩粉<br />\n再shake shake佢，成件事勁土炮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQu8uOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQu8uOj.png&h=891e471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地至在食下生果<br />\n所以全走。<br />\n喺我影張嘅時候，個小販叫我老婆俾杯野佢<br />\n落左少少野，之後我老婆食左啖<br />\n又俾佢再落多啲<br />\n可能佢以為自己食緊士多啤梨新地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKe8uPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKe8uPp.png&h=3e8a8ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我食左一粒，辣嘅，仲要幾辣下<br />\n好九唔搭八，甜搭辣，我只想要甜不辣<br />\n<br />\n最後要揸住杯野行返酒店用水喉水續粒洗<br />\n諗起都on_<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺越南啲人最中意踎街食野<br />\n好有風味<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38xxWvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38xxWvR.png&h=0b3b7482&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}